| ğŸ› ï¸ **Clan Creation**          | Any verified user can create a clan and become **Clan Head** (owner) |
| ğŸ‘¥ **Member Management**       | Add/invite members (by role) â†’ approve/reject â†’ assign permissions   |
| ğŸ” **Clan Visibility**         | Public (searchable) or Private (invite-only), shown in profiles      |
